Table__Delete__ActionRow: (state, extData, errors, event, rowData) => { (async function() {    const { data } = await extData.__?.httpClient?.deleteMethod(`configuration/FormDefinition/Delete?id=${rowData.Id}`);    })(); }
Search: (state, extData, errors, event) => { delete state.Table; extData.__?.setValueForm('Table', state); }
DialogAdd__BeforeOpenDialog: (state, extData, errors, event, tempState) => { return async function() {   const formRes = await formHelper.getFormByCode('Admin_FormDefinition_Add');     return {formDef: formRes }    }; }
DialogUpdate__BeforeOpenDialog: (state, extData, errors, event, tempState) => { return async function() { const formRes = await formHelper.getFormByCode('Admin_FormDefinition_Update');   const { data } = await extData.__?.httpClient?.getMethod(`configuration/FormDefinition/GetFormByCode?code=${tempState.Code}`); return {formDef: formRes, initState: data } }; }
